{
  "stem": "9878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She would not give it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She would say, I will keep it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And under penalty of death, the Germans, they, whenever they find gold, they will kill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they made the women and the young girls, [INAUDIBLE] to undress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The screaming, the hollering was terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Dogs and with whips they used to beat the people as you go around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They walked down into the-- into the grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The grave was 18 by-- by about 40 feet long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they made the people lay out like herrings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the Germans were sitting at the top of the graveside with the-- with the arm-- arms like [INAUDIBLE] like this, with the machine guns over [? their lap. ?] And they kept on shooting the people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Then a man went in-- inside the grave with big, long boots, and he kept on shooting whatever person was still moving.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Then they took another group, another group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They kept on taking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "This was going on for-- for several days and nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "At nighttime, when I was with the farmer, we saw the ghetto burning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "The farmer came into the-- to the-- to the barn where I was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And he says, kluku.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Kluku means a farmer boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Boy, run for your life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I can't keep you any longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I'm afraid, because the Germans gave an order, if anybody would give a-- give a Jew shelter, or give him a piece of bread to eat, they will kill the  whole family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I'm afraid for my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I was very good to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I kept you till now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I said-- And I took off, and I ran into the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Summer of 1942.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
